# Supabase & API

- Geo queries: PostGIS `ST_DWithin` or `ST_Distance` only
- `.select()` with explicit columns — never `*`
- Always `.limit()`; paginate pins (20 per page)
- RLS on every table

## Geo query example

```sql
SELECT id, user_id, title, location, visibility, pinned_at
FROM memory_pins
WHERE ST_DWithin(
  location,
  ST_Point($lon, $lat)::geography,
  $radiusMeters
)
AND visibility = 'public'
ORDER BY pinned_at DESC
LIMIT 20
```
